profile:
We're a team of trained roofing professionals that offer some of the most competitive pricing in Connecticut without jeopardizing service and work quality. At ADN, we purchase all of our products and materials directly from manufacturer and pass the savings on to you. We will never add, or hide charges. The initial quote will be the end price. When you choose ADN Roofing for your roofing needs, you can always rest assured that all of our employees have been hand-picked for experience, professionalism, competence and courtesy. No job is too small - call today for FREE estimate!
Proudly Serving Connecticut:  Stratford, Ansonia, Monroe, Trumbull, Shelton, Fairfield, Darien, Seymour, Oxford, Bridgeport, Bethany, Milford, Orange, Westport, Stamford, Derby, Norwalk, Ridgefield, Oxford, Prospect and more!

Our Services:
» Tear off and replacement
» Rip and plywood
» Flat roofs (epdm, mineral, rubber, recoating)
» Cedar shakes and asphalt shingles
» Skylights
» Chimneys (repairs and  flashing)
» Emergency repairs
» Snow removal
» Powerwashing
» Seamless gutters , cleaning , gutter guard  install

About Us:
» Over 15 Years in Business.
» Emergency Services Available.
» We utilize on the finest materials available.
» Affordable pricing with the top notch service.
» Offering the among the lowest pricing in the market.
» Free Estimates - Call Today!

Specialties:
Roofing, Gutters, Powerwashing, Chimney Repairs, Skylights

Visit: http://www.adnroofingct.com
Business Hours: Mon-Fri: 7:30am-5:00pm; Sat: 8:00am-4:00pm Sun:Closed
